title: I keep finishing my ranked Q, and I'm not able to connect after  the actual game begins to load.
body: internet is 100% working, I just got lower priority queue, because of something thats out of my hands?

replies.body: A common reason for not being able to connect to a match is if there are local network settings that conflict with League. To ensure this is not the case, I recommend working through our [**connection guide**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664-Troubleshooting-Connection-Issues). Should you run into further issues with connecting to matches after taking those steps, let me know!
